column5: WagJag Link  RideOnRentals.com  Hey guys! I love the idea of WagJag, but rarely come across anything worth while. This sounds decent.  $69 for 4hours(kinda short..) ice fishing hut rental for up to 12 people, here is what RideOnRentals.com says is included in the offer      Doesn't sound like too bad of a deal, especially if you want to go with first timers or kids to keep them warm.  My question is, what lake is it on? I am definitely interested to go with a group of people. At $70, bring 7-10 people and its pocket change per person.   What do you all think?
Sounds like a great deal,if you book the day(8hrs),that is still pocket change for 7-12 people for a great day on the lake fishing and being with friends.
I hate websites that advertise like mad but don't tell you where it is.
Well, since they are located in Wasaga Beach it would probably be safe to assume that you'd be fishing Georgan Bay.
